and E-Commerce Platform Business segments. It also offers CCAvenue, a payment gateway that enables merchants to easily and securely accept a wide range of digital payment methods, as well as payment gateway related solutions, including B2Biz payments, CCAvenue SNIP, CCAvenue TokenPay, CCAvenue F.R.I.S.K, CCAvenue TokenPay, and invoice payment and subscription solutions. In addition, the company provides BillAvenue, a unified and interoperable platform that enables seamless utility and recurring payments; ResAvenue, an online hospitality management solution that helps hoteliers to distribute room inventory; Go Payments, an online platform that offers domestic money transfer, AEPS, mobile recharge, travel bookings, and other financial services for consumers; and TrustAvenue, a lending platform that provide working capital loans, invoice/bill discounting, and early settlement to digital payment merchants and banks. Further, the company provides BuildaBazaar for Enterprise, a cloud based end-to-end software as a service eCommerce marketplace technology platform that allows corporates to transact online, manage the back end, make digital payments, undertake online marketing, and other value-added digital services. It operates in India, the United Arab Emirates, and internationally. The company was formerly known as Infibeam Avenues Limited and changed its name to AvenuesAI Limited in January 2026. AvenuesAI Limited was founded in 2001 and is headquartered in Gandhinagar, India."}}